Latest commit


* Block Shuffle Plugin Adds a plugin that simply takes all blocks in a selected area, and randomises their position. The plugin-view also got alphabetically sorted. * Block Shuffle Plugin (Update) Implemented an option to include Tile-Entities (off by default) (some special entities are still excluded when turned on). Optimized the options window.


