With a third-patty game editor, yes.


You can't change your skin color yet.


TerraSavr Is a web based inventory editing tool, which not only allows you to get items, but can also edit your character's appearance.


terrasavr is the best one, just know it doesn't preview the default clothing. http://terraria.gamepedia.com/Character_styles http://yal.cc/r/terrasavr/doc/


